Syncfusion Essential PDF WPF
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
Essential PDF is a .NET library capable of manipulating Adobe PDF files. It features a full-fledged object model for easily creating PDF files from any .NET language. It does not use any external libraries, and it is built from scratch in C#. 
